WEBVTT

00:00:37.300 --> 00:00:40.580
=Reincarnated Love=

00:00:40.780 --> 00:00:43.700
=Episode 14=

00:00:48.790 --> 00:00:50.030
(If Lu Huaijin)

00:00:50.280 --> 00:00:52.070
(is the mastermind behind all this,)

00:00:52.880 --> 00:00:53.840
(what will he do next?)

00:01:36.230 --> 00:01:37.920
What are you doing?

00:01:38.790 --> 00:01:39.630
Yuan,

00:01:40.640 --> 00:01:42.040
may peace follow you year after year

00:01:42.400 --> 00:01:43.590
with joy by your side.

00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:49.590
I've never told you about my birthday.

00:01:50.280 --> 00:01:51.510
How did you find out?

00:01:52.230 --> 00:01:53.760
I'm Huo Linchuan, after all.

00:01:54.150 --> 00:01:55.760
Is there anything I can't discover?

00:02:09.750 --> 00:02:11.270
ظآزThe dream shatteredظآز

00:02:11.630 --> 00:02:13.310
ظآزLike illusion, yet trueظآز

00:02:13.310 --> 00:02:14.950
ظآزLike a restless soulظآز

00:02:15.830 --> 00:02:17.390
ظآزHow vagueظآز

00:02:17.790 --> 00:02:19.310
ظآزRain and blood, drifting wildظآز

00:02:19.310 --> 00:02:21.550
ظآزA blade of frost in dreamsظآز

00:02:22.350 --> 00:02:24.950
ظآزLove and hate entwinedظآز

00:02:25.430 --> 00:02:28.270
ظآزRise and fall, yet never fadeظآز

00:02:31.120 --> 00:02:31.960
Yuan,

00:02:33.120 --> 00:02:34.310
the past misunderstandings

00:02:34.330 --> 00:02:35.680
ظآزWhen fate falls apartظآز

00:02:35.710 --> 00:02:37.240
have all faded like smoke and clouds.

00:02:39.080 --> 00:02:40.030
Today is your birthday.

00:02:41.520 --> 00:02:43.240
I swear here and now:

00:02:44.030 --> 00:02:45.143
For all the remaining years,

00:02:45.680 --> 00:02:47.840
I'll do everything to keep you safe

00:02:48.680 --> 00:02:49.593
and never abandon you.

00:02:51.030 --> 00:02:51.870
If I break my word...

00:02:52.240 --> 00:02:53.080
No need for oaths.

00:02:53.510 --> 00:02:57.590
ظآزStill, I refuse to bow or yieldظآز

00:02:57.670 --> 00:03:00.710
ظآزIn this life, love becomes my bladeظآز

00:03:00.870 --> 00:03:02.270
ظآزTo break free from reincarnationظآز

00:03:04.400 --> 00:03:05.240
Thank you,

00:03:06.870 --> 00:03:07.710
honey.

00:03:11.510 --> 00:03:14.310
ظآزIs this fate or calamityظآز

00:03:15.960 --> 00:03:17.000
Happy birthday,

00:03:17.560 --> 00:03:18.400
dear.

00:03:18.400 --> 00:03:22.150
ظآزI ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heartظآز

00:03:22.390 --> 00:03:25.310
ظآزIn the next life, grant me one kissظآز

00:03:25.430 --> 00:03:29.870
ظآزTo kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gazeظآز

00:03:30.070 --> 00:03:35.790
ظآزFor once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never partظآز

00:03:36.230 --> 00:03:38.950
ظآزThis fleeting life feels but a dreamظآز

00:03:39.190 --> 00:03:41.910
ظآزSober or indulgeظآز

00:03:42.960 --> 00:03:43.800
By the way,

00:03:44.400 --> 00:03:45.546
I have something to show you.

00:03:46.120 --> 00:03:46.960
What is it?

00:03:54.520 --> 00:03:55.520
What's this?

00:03:56.150 --> 00:03:57.680
This armor is called SilverScales.

00:03:58.150 --> 00:03:59.680
It followed my ancestors

00:03:59.960 --> 00:04:01.100
through hundreds of battles,

00:04:01.400 --> 00:04:02.340
protecting its master.

00:04:03.030 --> 00:04:04.240
It's a treasured heirloom

00:04:04.240 --> 00:04:05.750
of the Huo clan.

00:04:08.430 --> 00:04:09.270
Today,

00:04:10.280 --> 00:04:11.710
I wish to give it to you.

00:04:14.310 --> 00:04:15.150
This...

00:04:16.190 --> 00:04:18.000
This armor is so precious.

00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:20.430
It's also your family heirloom.

00:04:21.120 --> 00:04:21.960
I...

00:04:27.920 --> 00:04:29.830
You are the mistress of the Huo clan.

00:04:30.430 --> 00:04:32.070
And you are my wife.

00:04:34.040 --> 00:04:35.160
This armor protects

00:04:36.070 --> 00:04:38.270
the future matriarch of the Huo clan.

00:04:40.630 --> 00:04:41.830
But above all,

00:04:42.680 --> 00:04:44.190
you are Jiang Ruoli.

00:04:45.360 --> 00:04:47.160
You are the very heart of my life.

00:04:53.070 --> 00:04:53.910
If one day,

00:04:55.360 --> 00:04:56.560
trouble should befall me,

00:04:57.750 --> 00:04:59.310
let this armor keep you safe.

00:05:21.450 --> 00:05:23.170
ظآزWhere shall I seekظآز

00:05:23.480 --> 00:05:26.260
ظآزThe traces of your past livesظآز

00:05:27.200 --> 00:05:31.760
ظآزI'd spend a lifetime's luck
just for youظآز

00:05:32.770 --> 00:05:37.780
ظآزGazing at your figure
for the rest of my lifeظآز

00:05:38.010 --> 00:05:43.060
ظآزUntil time grows us oldظآز

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:48.690
ظآزDreams lift the night
where stars grow thinظآز

00:05:49.570 --> 00:05:54.770
ظآزWhen shall I meet you again
in another lifeظآز

00:05:55.090 --> 00:05:59.650
ظآزThe galaxy stirs;
destiny endlessly returnsظآز

00:05:59.990 --> 00:06:05.480
ظآزIf I could, let me guard you this timeظآز

00:06:05.480 --> 00:06:08.160
ظآزHow did this feeling beginظآز

00:06:08.410 --> 00:06:10.800
ظآزIn each trial, longing deepensظآز

00:06:11.070 --> 00:06:13.710
ظآزAcross vast lands, it still shinesظآز

00:06:13.850 --> 00:06:16.420
ظآزWhen the night fades,
the moon shines longerظآز

00:06:16.740 --> 00:06:19.280
ظآزA fleeting dream
shines through the rainظآز

00:06:19.530 --> 00:06:21.710
ظآزThrough three lifetimes,
we never partظآز

00:06:22.320 --> 00:06:27.730
ظآزA thousand years of snow
fall into your palmظآز

00:06:27.860 --> 00:06:30.320
ظآزHow does love fade awayظآز

00:06:30.730 --> 00:06:33.230
ظآزEach thought recalls the pastظآز

00:06:33.440 --> 00:06:36.060
ظآزLonging burns into a lasting acheظآز

00:06:36.270 --> 00:06:38.640
ظآزFrost stains the white robesظآز

00:06:39.070 --> 00:06:41.640
ظآزMist and clouds veil the skyظآز

00:06:41.850 --> 00:06:44.420
ظآزMy past was filled with you aloneظآز

00:06:44.630 --> 00:06:49.030
ظآزAll our joy and sorrow shapedظآز

00:06:49.280 --> 00:06:53.100
ظآزOur loveظآز

00:07:53.450 --> 00:07:54.970
ظآزThe dream shatteredظآز

00:07:55.330 --> 00:07:57.010
ظآزLike illusion, yet trueظآز

00:07:57.010 --> 00:07:58.650
ظآزLike a restless soulظآز

00:07:59.530 --> 00:08:01.090
ظآزHow vagueظآز

00:08:01.490 --> 00:08:03.010
ظآزRain and blood, drifting wildظآز

00:08:03.010 --> 00:08:05.250
ظآزA blade of frost in dreamsظآز

00:08:06.050 --> 00:08:08.650
ظآزLove and hate entwinedظآز

00:08:09.130 --> 00:08:11.970
ظآزRise and fall, yet never fadeظآز

00:08:12.610 --> 00:08:17.370
ظآزHow can I turn the tides
of this fleeting lifeظآز

00:08:17.970 --> 00:08:19.490
ظآزWhen fate falls apartظآز

00:08:19.890 --> 00:08:23.450
ظآزMemories return,
carving tears upon my faceظآز

00:08:24.170 --> 00:08:25.730
ظآزYet I can't hold onظآز

00:08:26.130 --> 00:08:29.850
ظآزOnly warmth remains
where longing once burnedظآز

00:08:30.570 --> 00:08:33.410
ظآزLife after lifeظآز

00:08:33.890 --> 00:08:36.570
ظآزFated to meet, but never meant to beظآز

00:08:37.210 --> 00:08:41.290
ظآزStill, I refuse to bow or yieldظآز

00:08:41.370 --> 00:08:44.410
ظآزIn this life, love becomes my bladeظآز

00:08:44.570 --> 00:08:45.970
ظآزTo break free from reincarnationظآز

00:08:45.970 --> 00:08:49.090
ظآزAll past affairs tangled with regretظآز

00:08:49.170 --> 00:08:50.610
ظآزNow shatter apartظآز

00:08:50.730 --> 00:08:54.490
ظآزBy fate and karmic ties confinedظآز

00:08:55.210 --> 00:08:58.010
ظآزIs this fate or calamityظآز

00:08:58.290 --> 00:09:01.130
ظآزIs it life, death, or parting painظآز

00:09:01.450 --> 00:09:05.850
ظآزI ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heartظآز

00:09:06.090 --> 00:09:09.010
ظآزIn the next life, grant me one kissظآز

00:09:09.130 --> 00:09:13.570
ظآزTo kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gazeظآز

00:09:13.770 --> 00:09:19.490
ظآزFor once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never partظآز

00:09:19.930 --> 00:09:22.650
ظآزThis fleeting life feels but a dreamظآز

00:09:22.890 --> 00:09:25.610
ظآزSober or indulgeظآز

00:09:26.050 --> 00:09:32.050
ظآزI only wish to be with you,
with all my heartظآز